    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s looking for a brand new home! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It runs great and has been well-loved! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Let's get you on the road!",
