    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This example boasts a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The double-VANOS system has been recently serviced, ensuring optimal cam timing and razor-sharp throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Equipped with a factory-spec variable M differential lock and a suspension geometry tuned for turn-in precision, this chassis remains highly communicative. It presents in honest, well-maintained condition, perfect for the purist seeking an analog driving experience with proven mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
