    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for all your weekend adventures? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well-loved. It\u2019s perfect for anyone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
