    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and the factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis retains its composure with a sophisticated five-link rear suspension and aluminum MacPherson strut front end. Recent service includes a full diagnostic of the VANOS actuators and a fresh oil service using 10W-60 synthetic. While showing minor signs of road use, the mechanical synchronization of the drivetrain and the integrity of the subframe remain excellent, offering a visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning pilot.",
